{"tid":1487999,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深圳灣武警集結係誤會","createTime":"2019-08-19T13:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T11:25:59.000Z","uid":268942,"like":13,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bd059e2fefd743ea6bbe5d072f48071b0091ed6f","tid":1487999,"uid":268942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:15:47.000Z","msg":"梁愛詩說,深圳灣武警集結不是針對香港騷亂,而是為國慶閱兵演練。原來武警操練時用粵語高呼&quot;後果自負&quot;,也是閱兵內容之一。想像北京大閱兵時會出現如下場面:習總說:&quot;同志們好。&quot;大兵回應:&quot;主席好!&quot;習說:&quot;同志們辛苦了！&quot;兵呼:&quot;後果自負!&quot;而且用粵語。"},{"pid":"cd748e1dcc1a2ea4742c4e438a99aa1df73f80ef","tid":1487999,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:16:26.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"76f8e0d9e3baa46f7bcfc6681e4d38972c7b86f3","tid":1487999,"uid":104804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:22:56.000Z","msg":"後果自負都係閱兵之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d595ce054cafba1909c4643a82143edbb29e8e3","tid":1487999,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:24:05.000Z","msg":"淆底呀，叫你嚟又唔嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eec2636c0d26d27a47087a7e430a3f7d0727df5","tid":1487999,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:25:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce072c4eb08c19a688f97438954a5c7dfb4c5993","tid":1487999,"uid":274680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:28:33.000Z","msg":"乜撚野丫，你到底up乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e66e3521a13863c6